channel.title: [508] ServerSoft DT [508]
channel.description:
Hello, this is the project of the [b]ServerSoft Development Team.[/b] Although our Development Team is [b][u]Not[/b] in place of advertisement on this website, it is still rapidly growing fast.
[ul]Some features on of our Base: [list][li]A Mapdata Class Base which makes it more unlikley for you to glitch in a Missing Mapdata region.[/li] [li]Anti SYI, and Anti Flooding. If we had a Vps, the Server would be Vitally impossible to crash with a Server Crasher.[/li] [li]Excellent Skilling Base, for each unique skill. Some skills are still under development, though.[/li] [li]100% Realistic Construction like real RuneScape. All rooms buildable, objects buildable, etc.[/li] [li]100% Anti-Lag (Only chance of you getting lag may be the cause of your own computer).[/li] [li]A backup Saving System, which automatically saves 3 backup character-types.[/li] [li]A new Grand Exchange, Absolutley NO ERRORS, and excacly like REAL RUNESCAPE.[/li] [/list]
And much, more!
We have been with ServerSoft for 3 years, however during those first 2 years, we were in 317. But during our past failures, we have learned from our mistakes, and decided to put our skills to our max. We have more features, but for some, we cannot take pictures of, but instead you must view the contents for yourself.
Here are some pictures of our Developments:
Grand Exchange:
[IMG]http://i11.servimg.com/u/f11/14/71/90/64/ge10.png[/img]
Clan Chat:
[IMG]http://i11.servimg.com/u/f11/14/71/90/64/cla10.png[/img]
Our Basic Shops:
[IMG]http://i11.servimg.com/u/f11/14/71/90/64/6510.png[/img]
Our newest Development:
[IMG]http://i11.servimg.com/u/f11/14/71/90/64/sc10.png[/img]
New Trading System:
[IMG]http://i11.servimg.com/u/f11/14/71/90/64/trad10.png[/img]
Like my Garden? JK, Construction =P:
[IMG]http://i11.servimg.com/u/f11/14/71/90/64/con110.png[/img]
Working BankTabs =):
[IMG]http://i11.servimg.com/u/f11/14/71/90/64/bt10.png[/img]
Construction 2:
[IMG]http://i11.servimg.com/u/f11/14/71/90/64/aaa10.png[/img]
Those were all of our pictures, (Don't worry, we have more developments, just no pics).
So what do you think? Do you like it? Do you think it's bad? Please, post here =) Posting will help us determin what the players like, and because of that, we can also decide what we should add, remove, or fix.
[b]50 Percent % Credits go to MoparScape Community user, Zack_Flowers, for the Construction Co-oordination.[/ul]
